# ============================================
# NOTES
# ============================================
# This .gitignore is designed for the Wiz Technical Exercise
# 
# Security reminders:
# - Never commit passwords or API keys
# - Never commit terraform.tfvars (use .example instead)
# - Never commit service account keys
# - Never commit .env files
# - Review each commit for sensitive data before pushing
#
# To check what's being tracked:
#   git status
#   git ls-files
#
# To remove a file that was accidentally committed:
#   git rm --cached <file>
#   git commit -m "Remove sensitive file"
#   git push
#
# Consider using git-secrets or gitleaks to prevent
# committing sensitive data:
#   https://github.com/awslabs/git-secrets
#   https://github.com/gitleaks/gitleaks
